    <published>2020-01-09T08:04:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-27T07:23:19.404Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>摘要：一些测试和 markdown 用法。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="2024-03-27-更新"><a href="#2024-03-27-更新" class="headerlink" title="2024.03.27 更新"></a>2024.03.27 更新</h1><p>几日不见, 这玩意儿变严格了. </p><p>从前突出一个懒散和随性采用</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!------------ more -----------&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写摘要, 如今这种写法在 <code>hexo s</code> 中失效了, 需采用严格的</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>默认的不支持直接使用 physics 包. 使用 <code>\require&#123;physics&#125;</code> 也没什么用 :skull: . </p><h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><h2 id="h2"><a href="#h2" class="headerlink" title="h2"></a>h2</h2><h3 id="h3"><a href="#h3" class="headerlink" title="h3"></a>h3</h3><h4 id="h4"><a href="#h4" class="headerlink" title="h4"></a>h4</h4><h5 id="h5"><a href="#h5" class="headerlink" title="h5"></a>h5</h5><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><p>脚注</p><p><sup><a href="#fn_脚注" id="reffn_脚注">脚注</a></sup>: </p><blockquote><p>引用</p></blockquote><h1 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h1><p>行内代码<code>代码</code></p><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">code</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="公式"><a href="#公式" class="headerlink" title="公式"></a>公式</h1><p>$\vec{r}$</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sin ^2 x+\cos ^2 x=1</script><p>实数集<code>\mathbb&#123;R&#125;</code>: $\mathbb{R}$  </p><p>占位符</p><p>quad空格<code>\quad</code>: $A\quad A$<br>两个quad空格<code>\qqaud</code>: $A\qquad A$</p><p>约等于<code>\approx</code>: $\approx$<br>大于等于<code>\geq</code>: $\geq$<br>小于等于<code>\leq</code>: $\leq$</p><p>正负<code>\pm</code>: $\pm$ (<code>\plusmn</code> mathjax 无法渲染)</p><h1 id="插入图片"><a href="#插入图片" class="headerlink" title="插入图片"></a>插入图片</h1><h2 id="一般情况"><a href="#一般情况" class="headerlink" title="一般情况"></a>一般情况</h2><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;<span class="symbol">%</span> asset_img <span class="number">0001.</span>jpg This <span class="built_in">is</span> an <span class="built_in">example</span> <span class="built_in">image</span> <span class="symbol">%</span>&#125;#失效</span><br><span class="line">![This <span class="built_in">is</span> an <span class="built_in">example</span> <span class="built_in">image</span>](./test/<span class="number">0001.</span>jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2020/01/09/test/0001.jpg" alt="This is an example image"></p><h2 id="自定义"><a href="#自定义" class="headerlink" title="自定义"></a>自定义</h2><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;width:70%;margin:auto&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">asset_img</span> 0001.jpg This is an example image %&#125;</span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div style="width:70%;margin:auto"><img src="/2020/01/09/test/01/09/test/0001.jpg" class title="This is an example image"></div><h1 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h1><p><a href="http://www.baidu.com" title="链接">链接</a></p><h1 id="使用内嵌-HTML-标签控制markdown颜色、字体、字号"><a href="#使用内嵌-HTML-标签控制markdown颜色、字体、字号" class="headerlink" title="使用内嵌 HTML 标签控制markdown颜色、字体、字号"></a>使用内嵌 HTML 标签控制markdown颜色、字体、字号</h1><h2 id="颜色"><a href="#颜色" class="headerlink" title="颜色"></a>颜色</h2><h3 id="字体颜色"><a href="#字体颜色" class="headerlink" title="字体颜色"></a>字体颜色</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#FF5566</span>&gt;</span>示例文字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font color="#FF5566">示例文字</font><h3 id="文字背景颜色"><a href="#文字背景颜色" class="headerlink" title="文字背景颜色"></a>文字背景颜色</h3><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">#003366</span>&gt;</span>示例文字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor="#003366">示例文字</td></tr></table><h2 id="字体"><a href="#字体" class="headerlink" title="字体"></a>字体</h2><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span>&gt;</span>示例文字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font face="微软雅黑">示例文字</font><h2 id="字号"><a href="#字号" class="headerlink" title="字号"></a>字号</h2><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">72</span>&gt;</span>示例文字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font size="72">示例文字</font><h2 id="综合"><a href="#综合" class="headerlink" title="综合"></a>综合</h2><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">#003366</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#FFFFFF</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">14</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">示例文字</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor="#003366"><font color="#FFFFFF" size="5" face="微软雅黑">示例文字</font></td></tr></table>]]></content>
    
    
